the Trent Krabbles,

as a guard,
things would be a little easier, but[ML:Dash ]

They say the mercenaries
there are all skilled.

rows.label: qst000106_msg008

[ML:Dash ]But the conversation got
sidetracked. I'll give you a reward
for protecting the cargo.
